Calculator for summary statistics for a list of doubles.

detaileddescription.para: Statistics are calculated by calling calculate() and passing a list of doubles. The individual statistics can then be retrieved using the associated methods. Note that not all statistics are calculated by default. Statistics which require slower computations are only calculated by specifying the statistic in the constructor or via setStatistics().
